ustific\u00e1bit ipse justus servus meus multos, et iniquit\u00e1tes e\u00f3rum ipse port\u00e1bit. Ideo disp\u00e9rtiam ei pl\u00farimos: et f\u00f3rtium d\u00edvidet sp\u00f3lia, pro eo, quod tr\u00e1didit in mortem \u00e1nimam suam, et cum sceler\u00e1tis reput\u00e1tus est: et ipse pecc\u00e1ta mult\u00f3rum tulit, et pro transgress\u00f3ribus rog\u00e1vit."
